        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【CES 2024】Samsung Odyssey OLED 電競螢幕，反應時間 0.03 ms GTG + 最高可達 360 Hz</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/10/ces-2024-samsung-odyssey-oled/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ces-2024-samsung-odyssey-oled</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/10/ces-2024-samsung-odyssey-oled/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:00:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Samsung Odyssey OLED]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電競]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1213831</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung 將在 CES 2024 推出全新頂級 Samsung Odyssey OLED 電競螢幕系列。新推出的 Odyssey OLED G9、Odyssey OLED G8 及 Odyssey OLED G6 搭載突破性的技術，向全球的電競玩家提供高質娛樂及工作體驗。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1214248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoleds-694x530.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="530" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoleds-694x530.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoleds-scaled.jpg 1177w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Samsung 推出 Odyssey OLED G9（型號：G95SD）、Odyssey OLED G8（型號：G80SD）和 Odyssey OLED G6（型號：G60SD），讓玩家全程投入享受遊戲體驗。</p><p>技術規格</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 144px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;"> </td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">Odyssey OLED G9</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">Odyssey OLED G8</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">Odyssey OLED G6</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">螢幕</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">49 吋超廣闊曲面電競顯示器</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">32 吋平面電競顯示器</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">27 吋 QHD 平面電競顯示器</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">解像度</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">DQHD (5,120&#215;1,440)</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">4K UHD (3,840&#215;2,160)</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">QHD (2,560&#215;1,440)</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">螢幕比例</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">32:9</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">16:9</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">16:9</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">刷新率</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">240 Hz</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">240 Hz</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">360 hZ</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px;">反應時間</td><td style="width: 25%; height: 24px; text-align: center;" colspan="3">0.03ms GTG</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Samsung 在 CES 2024 發布的 3 個新型號均配備 OLED 防眩光技術，有效減少光線反射，為用家提供更佳的觀看體驗，讓玩家在幾乎任何照明環境下都能享受一致的亮度和色彩，沉浸於遊戲世界中。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">全新 OLED 電競顯示器系列配備 VESA DisplayHDR True Black 400 技術，能夠呈現出更深邃的黑色及更鮮艷的色彩，除此之外亦同時支援 AMD FreeSync™ Premium Pro 技術，為玩家提供更流暢且延遲更低的 HDR 遊戲體驗。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1214253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-4-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-4-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Samsung Odyssey OLED G8</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">全新 Odyssey OLED 系列有 2 個 HDMI 2.1 插口、一個 DisplayPort 1.4 插口及一個 USB 集線器，讓玩家輕鬆連接各種裝置。此外，配備 VESA 掛牆架兼容的高度可調節支架（HAS）可以傾斜、旋轉及調節多個不同角度，讓用家可以按照自己需要調整不同角度，以獲得最佳觀看體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1214252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-3-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-3-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Samsung Odyssey OLED G6</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Core Lighting+技術能從螢幕背面發出環境光，讓玩家可以更加投入娛樂環境當中。機背搭配 Core Lighting+ 可提供多種顏色模式，讓螢幕更獨特具個性。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">與上一代型號（G95SC）相比，其照明圈纖幼了 4 倍。此外新款型號配備厚度僅為 3 mm 的纖薄金屬底座，無須任何工具即可組裝，而且能夠為用家節省桌面空間。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1214249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Samsung Odyssey 系列亦第一次推出平面螢幕，分別為 Odyssey OLED G8 及 G6。兩個螢幕均採用 16:9 比例。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1214251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-2-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-2-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Samsung Odyssey OLED G6</p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1214250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ces2024_odysseyoledg-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Samsung Odyssey OLED G8</p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/rog-phone-8-pro-first-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】ROG Phone 8 / 8 Pro　外形　手感　設計　規格開箱評測 + 與 ROG Phone 7 比對</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/nvidia-rtx-4070-super-unboxing/parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【開箱】NVIDIA RTX 4070 SUPER 顯示卡　搶先看 Founder Edition 真身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/10/ces-2024-samsung-ai/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】Samsung 發表 AI 螢幕，動作增強器 + 字幕朗讀</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/10/ces-2024-samsung-odyssey-oled/wireless-home/audio-visual/">【CES 2024】Samsung Odyssey OLED 電競螢幕，反應時間 0.03 ms GTG + 最高可達 360 Hz</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
